{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/\u041b\u043e\u0433\u043e.gif?t=1728558044\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About the Game</h2>Kronos is a tactical battle simulator, mixing elements of tactics, strategy, and intense first-person combat. In a world of endless war that\u2019s been raging for centuries, a war whose origins are long forgotten, the primary goal still remains clear. Defend your right to rule from enemy human commanders and their disposable, robotic armies. <br><br>The only choices left are to succeed or join the endless roster of would-be cosmic rulers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Disposable Army</h2><br>Manage personal disposable armies to take and control territory from the opposing faction. Lead robotic minions from the frontlines, personally issuing commands and praying that their tiny, electronic brains can handle the stress. Win the day before your silicon friends run out of combat spirit.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/\u041f\u043e\u043a\u0443\u043f\u043a\u0430_\u0434\u0440\u043e\u043d\u043e\u0432.gif?t=1728558044\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Non-Recyclable Foes</h2><br>An enemy army won\u2019t twiddle its metallic thumbs and wait. Do you turtle up defenses and risk losing momentum? Or run the razor-thin edge to victory, capturing just enough to keep the pressure on? Fortify each territory with turrets and upgrade leading bot to field a small, elite army? Perhaps try to attempt massive attacks of cheap, expendable robots? The quantity has a quality of its own.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/\u0411\u043e\u0439.gif?t=1728558044\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Skills to Master</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/\u0420\u0430\u0437\u043d\u043e\u